TITLE: Calculating Global Unrealized PnL for Shorts in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet shows how to estimate the global unrealized profit and loss (PnL) for all open short positions in a specific custody of the JLP pool. It uses the custody's global short sizes, global short average prices, and current token price.
