TITLE: Calculating Hourly Borrow Fee for Jupiter Perpetual Exchange Positions
DESCRIPTION: Formula for calculating the hourly borrow fee on Jupiter Perpetual Exchange. The fee is based on the proportion of tokens borrowed relative to the total tokens in the pool, multiplied by the hourly borrow rate and the position size.
SOURCE: https://github.com/jup-ag/docs/blob/main/Moved/2-perpetual-exchange/2-trading.md#2025-04-16_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
hourly borrow fee = (tokens borrowed / tokens in the pool) x hourly borrow rate x position size
```

